==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Excandescence
<hw>Ex`can*des"cence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>excandescentia</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A growing hot; a
white or glowing heat; incandescence.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Violent anger; a growing angry.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Blount.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Excandescent</ent>⟦br⟧
